SQL query of the view VMOR_MOR_MODELO_RELATORIO

SELECT MOR.MOR_ID, MOR.MOR_NM, MOR.MOR_CD_ATIVO
FROM SUP.MOR_MODELO_RELATORIO MOR
INNER JOIN sup.REL_RELATORIO_APS REL ON REL.MOR_ID = MOR.MOR_ID
INNER JOIN SUP.INE_INSPECAO_ENTIDADE INE ON INE.INE_ID = REL.REL_ID
WHERE INE.INE_CD_STATUS = 3 AND (INE.INE_DH_PUBLICACAO >= '2015-01-01' AND INE.INE_DH_PUBLICACAO < '2018-01-01')
